     <section class="section-dark section-hero"> 
      <div class="hero-copy article"> 
       <h1 class="col-offset-1 col-8 hero-title"> App Developers: Monetize Your Mobile Apps with AdMob </h1> 
      </div> 
     </section> 
     <section class="intro-sentence"> 
      <h3> AdMob, <a href="http://googlemobileads.blogspot.com/2011/09/admob-is-for-mobile-app-developers.html" target="_blank">not to be confused with Adsense</a>, is a mobile app advertising platform designed specifically for app developers. AdMob helps app developers monetize their mobile apps by showing ads in their mobile apps. </h3> 
     </section> 
     <div class="cols-row col-offset-1 position-rel article-content"> 
      <div class="col-10"> 
       <!--[if !IE]> --> 
       <picture class="icon">
